Chorus: 
Vair me o, ro van o 
Vair me o, ro van ee 
Vair me o, o ru o ho 
Sad am I without thee When I'm lonely, dear white heart 
Black the night and wild the sea 
By love's light my foot finds 
The old pathway to thee. Chorus Thou'rt the music of my heart 
Harp of joy, o cruit mo chridh 
Moon of guidance by night 
Strength and light thou'rt to me